---
import { Image } from "astro:assets";
import Base from "../layouts/Base.astro";
import websiteHero from "../assets/images/website-hero.png";
---

<Base title="About" description="Summit Ledger Books specializes in bookkeeping for real estate investors, property managers, and developers. Learn about our mission and values.">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="about-hero">
      <Image src={websiteHero} alt="Austin, founder of Summit Ledger Books" class="about-hero-img" />
    </div>
    <h1 class="section-heading">About Summit Ledger Books</h1>

    <div class="prose">
      <p>Summit Ledger Books was founded with a simple belief: real estate investors and property managers deserve accurate, affordable bookkeeping that actually understands their business. Too many owners spend their evenings wrestling with spreadsheets instead of evaluating their next deal or managing their properties.</p>

      <p>We started Summit Ledger Books to change that. Based in Kaysville, Utah, we specialize in real estate accounting and partner with investors, property managers, and developers across Davis County, Salt Lake County, and throughout the state to keep financial records organized, accurate, and ready for tax season, lenders, or any audit.</p>

      <h2>Our Values</h2>

      <ul>
        <li><strong>Accuracy:</strong> Your books need to be right. We double-check every entry and reconciliation.</li>
        <li><strong>Transparency:</strong> No hidden fees, no surprises. You'll always know exactly what you're paying for.</li>
        <li><strong>Reliability:</strong> We meet every deadline, every month. Your books are never behind.</li>
        <li><strong>Simplicity:</strong> We explain your finances in plain language, not accounting jargon.</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Who We Serve</h2>

      <p>We specialize in bookkeeping for real estate investors, property managers, real estate developers, and agents. Whether you own a single rental property, manage a portfolio of units, or are developing your next project, we understand the financial complexity of real estate and know how to keep your books clean, organized, and audit-ready. See our full list of <a href="/services">bookkeeping services</a> to learn what we handle.</p>

      <p>Read our <a href="/blog">blog</a> for practical guidance on real estate bookkeeping, tax preparation, and portfolio management.</p>

      <p>Ready to take bookkeeping off your plate? <a href="/contact">Book a free consultation.</a></p>
    </div>

  </div>
</Base>
